players.name: Riley Watts
players.bio: Oldest on the team and a natural born leader: hoovalicious(riley watts) leads his teammates to great heights. His rage knows no bounds when it comes to enemy players flaming and trolling.

players.name: Brady Watts
players.bio: Second oldest and also a natural leader: wheatylicious rides waves of glory and inspires his teammates to be the best versions of themselves. Durable and light-hearted, wheatylicious brings a calming/centering energy to the team.
players.catchPhrase: This is gonna be a blast

players.name: Cary Watts
players.bio: A worthwhile alternate: tehoovalitious knows no bounds when it comes to exploration. While mechanical skills are up to par, macro strategy falls by the way-side. Tehooalitious brings the much needed wild-card element that inspires all.
players.division: Bronze III, Silver I at heart

players.name: Dugan Watts
players.bio: Small but mighty: shoovalicious is surely a wonder child. This hot-shot hits his shots and knows what to do and how to do it. He can carry and support, whatever the team needs. His light-hearted humor keeps morale high and spirits bright. Watch out for this one

players.name: Brad Barrow
players.bio: New kid on the block: Brad Barrow has solidified his spot with dedication and resourcefulness. He does his research and executes when the time comes.
players.division: Silver I, Gold V at heart

players.name: Joe Watts
players.bio: Sir Scrub & bubbles himself: crazy joe is old school. He doesn't play much but he knows how to watch and annoy the team. His insights are short but numerous, but we love having him around.
